IncidentSuppNarrative.NarrativeText: Attachments -NCMEC Cybertip # 182658298 Narrative On January 8, 2024, the Maryland State Police Computer Crimes Section /Maryland Internet Crimes Against Children Task Force received NCMEC CyberTip #182658298. The CyberTip, generated by Google, indicated that a subject was uploading/possessing/distributing child pornography through the internet. The CyberTip was assigned to TFC Burnett for investigation. The CyberTip provided the following information pertaining to the suspect: Name: Erika Garcia Mobile Phone: +12162588219 (Verified 12-20-2022 05:03:02 UTC) Date of Birth: 09-29-1981 Email Address: erikafeliciano929@gmail.com (Verified) TFC Burnett reviewed this Cybertip and observed it to contain two reported video files that depicts child pornography as it is defined by Maryland Law and appear to be self produced. The file is described below: Filename: dw1O0yeA624.mp4 Description: This file is an eleven second colored video of a Hispanic male child wearing an orange shirt and black/red plaid pants around his ankle, listening to music. The child is seen exposing his penis to the camera while he moves around. Based on the size and physical characteristics, the child appears to be 7-9 years old. Upload: 2607:fb91:1488:9e9e:fcde:3a85:d16b:bd29 on 12-17-2023 at 23:02:15 UTC Filename: P_j1onYNCy4.mp4 Description: This file is a twelve second colored video of the same Hispanic male child as the other video. The child is wearing an orange shirt and black/red plaid pants, listening to music. The child is seen pulling his pants down, exposing his buttocks to the camera while he moves around. Based on the size and physical characteristics, the child appears to be 7-9 years old. Upload: 2607:fb91:1488:9e9e:fcde:3a85:d16b:bd29 on 12-17-2023 at 22:51:12 UTC TFC Burnett used an open source search for IP address reported on the Cybertip. The upload IP (2607:fb91:1488:9e9e:fcde:3a85:d16b:bd29) is registered through T-Mobile and geo-locates to Baltimore, MD. There are numerous other IP addresses. On 1/9/2024, at approximately 1117 hours, TFC Burnett attempted to contact the Google account holder by phone (1216258821) but the number was out of service. TFC Burnett authored a subpoena for the IP addresses relating to MD (T-Mobile), which was submitted to the Howard County States Attorneys Office fore endorsement. Case Status Case open, investigation ongoing.
